	<description>
		<p>Pioneer is a space adventure game set in our galaxy at the
			turn of the 31st century.
		</p>

		<p>The game is open-ended, and you are free to eke out whatever
			kind of space-faring existence you can think of. Explore
			and trade between millions of star systems. Turn to a
			life of crime as a pirate, smuggler or bounty hunter.
			Travel through the territories of various factions
			fighting for power, freedom or self-determination. The
			universe is whatever you make of it.
		</p>

		<p>Pioneer is under constant development and has a friendly
			community of players, modders and developers around it.
			We'd love for you to try it and make part of the galaxy
			your own!
		</p>
	</description>

